snippet: Pinch-hitter Colby Rasmus homered in the 10th inning and the Toronto Blue Jays earned their first three-game sweep at Tampa Bay by beating the Rays 1-0 on Thursday night....

headline.print_headline: Rasmus Homers in 10th, Blue Jays Beat Rays 1-0
headline.main: Rasmus Homers in 10th, Blue Jays Beat Rays 1-0

lead_paragraph: Pinch-hitter Colby Rasmus homered in the 10th inning and the Toronto Blue Jays earned their first three-game sweep at Tampa Bay by beating the Rays 1-0 on Thursday night.
